This …

~~~ .php
Hook::NS('foo.bar.baz', [$a, $b]);
~~~

… is equal to this:

~~~ .php
Hook::fire(['foo.bar.baz', 'bar.baz', 'baz'], [$a, $b]);
~~~

… is equal to these:

~~~ .php
Hook::fire('foo.bar.baz', [$a, $b]);
Hook::fire('bar.baz', [$a, $b]);
Hook::fire('baz', [$a, $b]);
~~~